column3: Ah, <If(PlayerParameter(4))>Miss<Else/>Mister</If> <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,2)/>. I have your furnishings right here, if you wish to reclaim them.
In the event you are...divested of your private chambers, we shall collect your furnishings for safekeeping.
Pray speak with me to reclaim your furnishings should this regrettable circumstance come to pass.
